{"title":"mysql的访问设置","date":"2019-11-03T16:00:00.000Z","link":"2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置","tags":["mysql"],"updated":"2019-11-09T02:01:43.980Z","content":"<p>Docs</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"远程连接mysql\">远程连接mysql<a href=\"2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置#远程连接mysql\"></a></h3><blockquote>\n<p>本意是为了将MySQL放到ECS服务器，本地不用开mysql服务了，好处呢</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果本机关机不用每次都重开启服务</li>\n<li>数据能有一个备份</li>\n<li>可以缓解本机的内存压力</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"开启服务器权限：\">开启服务器权限：<a href=\"2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置#开启服务器权限：\"></a></h3><p>不管是阿里云，还是腾讯云他们的端口都没有默认开放<code>3306</code>端口，需要手动开启</p>\n<h3 id=\"设置mysql的配置文件\">设置mysql的配置文件<a href=\"2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置#设置mysql的配置文件\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /etc/mysql/mysql.conf.d</span><br><span class=\"line\">vi mysql.conf -- <span class=\"comment\">#bind-address =127.0.0.1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"更改库字段\">更改库字段<a href=\"2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置#更改库字段\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql -u root -p</span><br><span class=\"line\">use mysql;</span><br><span class=\"line\">select user, host from user;</span><br><span class=\"line\">update user set host=&apos;%&apos; where user=&apos;root&apos;</span><br><span class=\"line\">flush privileges;</span><br><span class=\"line\">GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO &apos;root&apos;@&apos;%&apos; IDENTIFIED BY &apos;yourpwd&apos; WITH GRANT OPTION;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"mysql 探究","link":"2019/11/08/mysql 探究"},"next":{"title":"面试准备复习","link":"2019/11/01/面试准备复习"},"plink":"http://jccjd.top/2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置/","copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://jccjd.top/2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置/\" title=\"mysql的访问设置\">http://jccjd.top/2019/11/04/mysql的访问设置/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}